item.title: The detective, the professor and early media RTP
item.description: “You have to dial an access code to pick up your messages.” Sophie Neveu says to professor Langdon. After a confused look he dials the three digit access code written on the paper Mrs. Neveu gave him. The secret message he hears changes everything…
